<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="instant-n">instant <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɪnstənt/    美 /'ɪnstənt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-moment">1.★ <strong>瞬间；即刻 (moment)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I couldn't answer <strong>for an instant</strong>.
我一时答不上来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>In an instant</strong>, he took off his coat and jumped into the water.
他立即脱下外衣，跳入水中。</p><footer>2010 陕西</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="the-instant-that">the instant (that)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>一…就：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The instant (= As soon as) she stopped asking questions, I got up and went out of the room.
她一停止问问题，我就起身走出了房间。</p><footer>北师大⑤ – 14</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>instantly /'ɪnstəntli/ adv   </p></div>